description.en:
"Go to the pond and steal one of the robes of the celestial beings. They will grant you a wish to get it back!" "That's... blackmailing, right?" 

Cheongyeon, a magical being who can turn into a deer, was being chased down by a hunter! While running away, a woodcutter helps him escape that horrible destiny... Cheongyeon becomes interested in this mysterious man and plans a trick to kidnap him. However, little does he know that this woodcutter's axe isn't used to cut wood, but to cut people!

description.ko:
「연못에서 목욕 중인 선인의 날개옷을 뺏고 소원을 비세요!」

「그거… 공갈·협박이잖아?」

사냥꾼에게 쫓기던 자신의 목숨을 구해준 나무꾼에게 폭 빠지고 만 사슴 수인 청연.
순진한 얼굴로 초대를 빙자한 납치 계획을 세우는 청연이 모르는 사실이 있었으니…
나무꾼의 정체는 도끼로 사람을 잡는 도적이라는 것!
